=== 主校区 ===
亨特学院的主校区位于东68街与莱星顿大道交界，包括东大楼，西大楼，北大楼以及托马斯·亨特堂，各大楼之间以空中走廊相连接。校区的地理位置优越，步行数分钟即可到达中央公园，附近也有很多纽约市的文化名胜，诸如[[纽约大都会博物馆|大都会艺术博物馆]]，[[亞洲協會|亚洲协会]]及其博物馆以及[[弗里克收藏|弗里克收藏馆]]。学校底下即为纽约地铁6号线的68街站点。亨特学院下的科学与艺术学院以及教育学院进驻于主校区内。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hunter.cuny.edu/abouthunter/maps/68th-street-main-campus|title=68th Street (Main Campus) — Hunter College|accessdate=2016-07-04|work=www.hunter.cuny.edu|archive-date=2017-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171115103343/http://www.hunter.cuny.edu/abouthunter/maps/68th-street-main-campus|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 卫星校区 ===
亨特学院下辖两个卫星校区：Silberman社会工作学院大楼以及布鲁克戴尔校区。Silberman社会工作学院大楼位于东118及119节与三大道交界，Silberman社会工作学院及公共卫生学院进驻于内。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hunter.cuny.edu/abouthunter/maps/silberman-school-of-social-work-school-of-urban-public-health|title=Silberman School of Social Work/School of Urban Public Health/Centro — Hunter College|accessdate=2016-07-04|work=www.hunter.cuny.edu|archive-date=2017-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105055654/http://www.hunter.cuny.edu/abouthunter/maps/silberman-school-of-social-work-school-of-urban-public-health|dead-url=no}}</ref>布鲁克戴尔校区位于东25街与一大道交界，亨特-贝尔维尤护理学院，医疗专业学校（School of Health Professions）及医疗专业图书馆等皆进驻于内。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hunter.cuny.edu/abouthunter/maps/brookdale-campus|title=Brookdale Campus/ Hunter-Bellevue School of Nursing/ School of Health Professions  — Hunter College|accessdate=2016-07-04|work=www.hunter.cuny.edu|archive-date=2018-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181123080050/http://www.hunter.cuny.edu/abouthunter/maps/brookdale-campus|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 学术及排名 ==
亨特学院受美国中部教育协会（Middle States Commission on Higher Education）认证，下设的各学位也有各自的学术机构认证。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://catalog.hunter.cuny.edu/content.php?catoid=25&navoid=5300|title=Accreditation - Hunter College - Acalog ACMS™|accessdate=2016-07-04|work=catalog.hunter.cuny.edu|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106080722/http://catalog.hunter.cuny.edu/content.php?catoid=25&navoid=5300|dead-url=no}}</ref>学校提倡学生接受广泛的文理教育（liberal arts）；无论专业如何，所有亨特学院的学生都必须完成12学分的“pluralism and diversity”（多元化社会）课程要求。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://catalog.hunter.cuny.edu/preview_program.php?catoid=6&poid=754|title=List of Approved Courses for the GER Pluralism and Diversity Requirement|accessdate=2016-07-04|work=catalog.hunter.cuny.edu|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106080724/http://catalog.hunter.cuny.edu/preview_program.php?catoid=6&poid=754|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hunter.cuny.edu/senate/curriculum-review-and-approval-1/appendix-a|title=Appendix A: Catalog Description of the Hunter Core Requirement — Hunter College|accessdate=2016-07-04|work=www.hunter.cuny.edu|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106080719/http://www.hunter.cuny.edu/senate/curriculum-review-and-approval-1/appendix-a|dead-url=no}}</ref>

亨特学院是纽约市立大学系统内招生最严格的学院之一。2014年秋季录取率为34.8%。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/hunter-college-2689/applying|title=CUNY--Hunter College {{!}} Hunter College {{!}} Applying {{!}} Best College {{!}} US News|accessdate=2016-07-04|work=colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816153211/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/hunter-college-2689/applying|dead-url=no}}</ref>

亨特学院以其出色的大学教育及低廉的学费而闻名，连续三年被普林斯顿评论（Princeton Review）评为“十大最具性价比的公立大学”之一。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.hunter.cuny.edu/communications/pressroom/news/hunter-is-named-201cbest-value-college201d-for-third-straight-year|title=Hunter is Named “Best Value College” for Third Straight Year — Hunter College|accessdate=2016-07-04|work=www.hunter.cuny.edu|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106080736/http://www.hunter.cuny.edu/communications/pressroom/news/hunter-is-named-201cbest-value-college201d-for-third-straight-year|dead-url=no}}</ref>

